{"tid":1417861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日發夢係天水圍發生呢樣野","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T18:12:08.000Z","uid":9051,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4729638a3329a4dd0e2a89d158bf6740d70ee800","tid":1417861,"uid":9051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:20:35.000Z","msg":"各位<br />\n<br />\n我唔係想分化 亦都明白各有各做呢個道理<br />\n<br />\n但今日天水圍一役 我真係好想屌你呢個肥婆<br />\n<br />\n今日發夢中午30人被捕後 狗仔推到天耀商場<br />\n你就叫人走去屯門 簡簡單單be water 有狗咪快閃 敵進我退 但唔係退到第二個戰場囉 仲要叫物資走<br />\n<br />\n經過琴晚少女單野 我相信大家目標應該係天水圍狗署 <br />\n<br />\n再到夜晚 我又見到你係天水圍 搞咩魚絲欄 話阻防暴阻狗車 仲到我講前線手足會知 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌 你 老 母</span></span><br />\n<br />\n即刻有手足比魚絲kick到 我都唔撚知你係想伏狗定伏手足 再者前線手足唔單止狗署前既手足 天盛個邊仲有記者同其他手足 <br />\n<br />\n如果速龍衝出黎再捉人 情況一定混亂 混亂之下邊個會睇到無色魚絲 你仲同我講 前幾次發夢都有咁用 <br />\n<br />\n屌你老尾 我咁多次發夢都未見過咁樣set係自己手足後面既路障<br />\n<br />\n而紅色鐵欄 我唔知係咪你做 我唔會怪落你度<br />\n<br />\n個條路就得行人路同輕鐵既路 大部分手足係個邊聚集 咁樣set鐵欄防狗定防人 就真係不得而知<br />\n <br />\n我明白大家開始接受到勇武 個個想做勇武 但唔該set路障同陷阱 唔好累到自己手足 唔想再見到有手足係我面前救唔到 而原因係因為自己友set錯野而造成<br />\n<br />\nBtw 多謝你拉住我 姐姐/妹妹 記得著返長褲啦 保護好自己先可以長期抗爭 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！ 時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n黃色：手足<br />\n黑色：魚絲<br />\n紅色：鐵欄<br />\n綠色：街坊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eDDxA2J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeDDxA2J.png&h=e30fc369&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e596d8afc724b5b1398827930ea6665f082c294c","tid":1417861,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:20:50.000Z","msg":"建議］ p牌正負評顯示<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1415247</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"df302ea97c80b15edab5bc47d2e5d6f49da020aa","tid":1417861,"uid":272976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:21:34.000Z","msg":"到底我哋仲要放棄幾多嘢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417655\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417655</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1b1907f72cffb60ce846b7f42f0d09c7475f7f36","tid":1417861,"uid":164705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:21:43.000Z","msg":"真係好柒 ....<br />\n你set就通知大圍啦仆街<br />\n陰9自已人"},{"pid":"fb2f1a5757331c3f4ddd16614f844497f7e91140","tid":1417861,"uid":9051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b1907f72cffb60ce846b7f42f0d09c7475f7f36","tid":1417861,"uid":164705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:21:43.000Z","msg":"真係好柒 ....<br />\n你set就通知大圍啦仆街<br />\n陰9自已人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:23:31.000Z","msg":"推撚到個個睇到 唔好再累到前線手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5cdfd6d1d6cfe5fa8f7ca62c8848ec0a43427ac","tid":1417861,"uid":9051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:24:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"259fcdab438de5481281f7dac4d5d6220194470a","tid":1417861,"uid":9051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:24:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec909fbd31b3f1d4068d9e91b4a67d04e4bb9d50","tid":1417861,"uid":9051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:25:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76c361b697094f59ada6a109565cd5969e4b3e6d","tid":1417861,"uid":164043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:25:18.000Z","msg":"有無人受傷"},{"pid":"d427eac7199affd861726f9f34581d3b508a5a73","tid":1417861,"uid":9051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76c361b697094f59ada6a109565cd5969e4b3e6d","tid":1417861,"uid":164043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:25:18.000Z","msg":"有無人受傷"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:27:00.000Z","msg":"隔左一陣 我同啲人已經𠝹斷哂<br />\n但地下仲有魚絲 會左腳ki